"      </i>",
"      , 2007, 110(4):941-56.",
"      <span class=\"pubmed-id\">",
"       [PubMed",
"       <a href=\"UTD.htm?7/61/8152/abstract-text/17906043/pubmed\" id=\"17906043\" target=\"_blank\">",
